  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over low heat.",
    "Add the ginger paste, galangal paste, and chili flakes. Cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the curry powder and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the red snapper fillet, cook for 3-4 minutes per side. Remove from heat and set aside.",
    "Add the sweet potato noodles, coconut milk, and fish sauce (if using) to the skillet. Cook for 3-4 minutes.",
    "Stir in the lime juice and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the chopped coriander to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Serve the noodles hot, topped with the cooked red snapper fillet."
